<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, September 14 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock
Exchange National-100 Index closed at 2,304.97 on Monday, down
23.70 points, or 1.00 percent, from Friday's finish.
</P>
<P>
The trading was heavy with the turnover reaching over 40
trillion Turkish Liras (over 144 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The industrial index went down 29.79 points, or 1.41 percent,
to close at 1,906.25 points, and the service index fell 95.04
points, or 3.15 percent, to close at 2,874.13 points, while the
financial index went up 0.44 points, or 0.03 percent, to close at
2,871.45 points. 
</P>
</TEXT>
