<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, September 12 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at
Tehran Stock Exchange on Monday stood at 1519.93 points, up 2.51
points compared to that on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
