arrival of an Egyptian large medical team under Egyptian Health
Minister here "is a generous gesture from Egyptian President Hosni
Mubarak and an indication of the strong ties between the peoples
of the two countries."
</P>
<P>
An Egyptian aircraft arrived here Monday morning carrying an
Egyptian high-level delegation under Minister of Health as well as
a quantity of medicines.
</P>
<P>
