the Peace Tower early Monday morning.
</P>
<P>
He threatened to ignite a propane tank and a gasoline can in
the front seat if he was not allowed to meet with Chretien.
</P>
<P>
In a note left with a local radio station, the man said he
suffered emotional problems due to a head injury in military
training.
</P>
<P>
After about two hours of discussion with police negotiators,
the man finally dropped his plan and was taken to hospital, the
reports said. 
</P>
</TEXT>
