the the Group of Seven (G7) industrial nations on how to deal with
the serious global financial situation.
</P>
<P>
Brown, due to pay a brief visit to Japan Wednesday, told
reporters that Japan, the world's second-largest economy, was a
key engine for growth in Asia and the rest of the world.
