<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, September 15 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock
Exchange National-100 Index closed at 2,198.95 on Tuesday, down
106.03 points, or 4.64 percent, from Monday's finish.
</P>
<P>
The turnover stood at 31.5 trillion Turkish Liras (114.5
million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The financial index dropped 116.41 points, or 4.09 percent,
to close at 2,755.05 points, the industrial index fell 78.31
points, or 4.13 percent, to close at 1,827.94 points, and the
service index tumbled 217.53 points, or 7.70 percent, to close
at 2,656.60 points. 
</P>
